main event: A civilian witnessed a bright white object in the sky in New Carlisle, Ohio on August 9, 1966.
interesting points: The object was observed for 1 minute during the night,The witness reported clear weather and a clear sky at the time of observation,There was no physical evidence found related to the sighting,The object was described as appearing solid and bright white,The witness reported having seen a similar object before in August 23, 1956.
